flowchart TD
    A[docs-gen input<br/>repoId + repoPath + repoTree] --> B[File discovery]
    B --> C[Classification<br/>code markdown csv text]
    C --> D[Language detection for code]

    D --> E{Loader selection}
    E --> E1[AST loader for code<br/>with textual fallback]
    E --> E2[Markdown loader]
    E --> E3[CSV loader]
    E --> E4[Text loader]

    E1 --> F[Chunking]
    E2 --> F
    E3 --> F
    E4 --> F

    F --> G[Build indexable documents<br/>text + metadata]
    G --> H[Generate embeddings]
    H --> I[Upsert vectors into Qdrant<br/>single collection]

    I --> J[Section retrieval query<br/>title + description + relevant_files]
    J --> K[Qdrant similarity search<br/>mandatory filter: repo_id]
    K --> L[Context builder<br/>dedupe + group by file + trim]

    L --> M[Writer agent<br/>generate markdown section]
    M --> N[Persist file<br/>/wiki_output/{repo_id}/NN-section.md]

    subgraph Metadata required per chunk
      O1[repo_id]
      O2[file_path]
      O3[file_kind]
      O4[language]
      O5[chunk_type]
      O6[start_line end_line]
      O7[pipeline_version]
    end

    G --> O1
    G --> O2
    G --> O3
    G --> O4
    G --> O5
    G --> O6
    G --> O7
